About Me.

Hi, I’m Brielle—a passionate problem solver, product enthusiast, and lifelong learner. With a dual degree in Business Administration from the Ivey School of Business and Computer Science from Western University, I thrive at the intersection of technology and innovation. ​ My experiences range from product management at Appen to product marketing at Deloitte and software engineering at S &P Global, giving me a diverse perspective on creating solutions that drive impact. ​ I believe in the power of technology to create equitable opportunities, and I’m driven by a mission to build products that help others grow and succeed. ​ Explore my portfolio, connect with me, and let’s create something impactful together!
